The '''Endregaad Plague''' was a virulent disease that arose on the planet [[Endregaad]]. Symptoms included fever, extreme loss of bodily fluids, crusting around the eyes and mouth, and the swelling of the tongue and fingers. After close examination, it was concluded that, while non-fatal, no species was naturally immune to the disease. Medicinal [[Spice/Legends|spice]] was found to combat the disease, but multiple treatments were required to prevent relapse. Pending further study, it was learned that the plague was a mutated form of a virus native to the planet [[Varl/Legends|Varl]].

